---
layout: base.njk
title: Notes
description: Short notes on what I'm thinking — observations, half-formed ideas, and things worth writing down.
permalink: /blog/
---
<div class="container">

  <header class="page-header">
    <div class="eyebrow"><span class="eyebrow-dot"></span> pris.la / notes</div>
    <h1>Short notes on<br /><em>what I'm thinking.</em></h1>
    <p>Observations, half-formed ideas, and things worth writing down.</p>
  </header>

  <div class="post-feed">
    {%- for post in collections.notes %}
      <div class="post-item">
        <div class="post-item-meta">
          {% if post.data.tag %}<span class="tag">{{ post.data.tag }}</span>{% endif %}
          <span class="post-date">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</span>
        </div>
        {% if post.data.title %}<h2>{{ post.data.title }}</h2>{% endif %}
        <div class="post-body">{{ post.templateContent | safe }}</div>
      </div>
    {%- endfor %}
  </div>

</div>
